value.snippet: New Logo. Along with the revamped site, I have created a new logo to go with it; it is probably the best looking thing I have ever drawn. The logo takes inspiration from the IBM PCJr with a few more rounded corners, thinner bezels, and a more minimalist feel. It was made in Inkscape with the basic shapes and the font is Roboto Mono.
